00:03:04,180 --> 00:03:06,982
because when you refer to, say,

38
00:03:07,651 --> 00:03:11,973
you know, a mouse card or a mouse suit in the rules,

39
00:03:12,494 --> 00:03:14,515
people need to be able to look at the table

40
00:03:14,575 --> 00:03:17,596
and recognize that mouse icon as being a mouse.

41
00:03:19,918 --> 00:03:23,280
And so here are four suits.

42
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:27,322
We have our foxes, our bunnies, our mice, and our birds.

43
00:03:27,342 --> 00:03:29,263
And here's the new mouse.

44
00:03:29,783 --> 00:03:32,905
So after we did that icon testing,

45
00:03:32,965 --> 00:03:36,006
we came up with a new concept for a mouse icon.

