49
00:03:51,162 --> 00:03:58,084
And to the point where now this idea of the monkey mouse icon has become somewhat of a

50
00:03:58,164 --> 00:04:04,045
touchstone for places where Kyle thinks that something is a bad idea, basically.

51
00:04:05,502 --> 00:04:09,043
But we put this new mouse icon in front of people,

52
00:04:09,684 --> 00:04:13,166
and invariably people would say, oh, it's a mouse.

53
00:04:13,206 --> 00:04:15,547
People understood what this new icon was.

