00:05:44,477 --> 00:05:54,620
close by, the whiskers just do not show up in other contexts, especially on our game

74
00:05:54,660 --> 00:05:59,142
board when the icon is scaled down and it has this darker background.

75
00:05:59,162 --> 00:05:59,982
Because

76
00:06:00,585 --> 00:06:04,567
Whiskers just kind of just kind of get reduced into oblivion

